'''Google Fi'''是[[Google|Google]]旗下的[[移动虚拟运营商|移动虚拟运营商]]（MVNO），通过[[T-Mobile|T-Mobile]]和[[Sprint|Sprint]]的Wi-Fi和[[蜂窩行動網路|蜂窩行動網路]]向美国以及超过200个国家和地区的漫游用户提供语音及数据服务<ref name="google-blog-say-hi-to-fi">{{cite web | url=https://googleblog.blogspot.com/2015/04/project-fi.html | title=Say hi to Fi: A new way to say hello | publisher=Google | work=Official Google Blog | date=2015-04-22 | accessdate=2015-12-05 | author=Fox, Nick | archive-date=2020-09-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916202611/https://googleblog.blogspot.com/2015/04/project-fi.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="forbes-google-unveils-wireless">{{cite web | url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/ellenhuet/2015/04/22/google-unveils-wireless-service-project-fi/ | title=Google Unveils Its 'Project Fi' Wireless Service | publisher=Forbes.com LLC | work=Forbes | date=2015-04-22 | accessdate=2015-12-05 | author=Huet, Ellen | archive-date=2016-11-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161129152041/http://www.forbes.com/sites/ellenhuet/2015/04/22/google-unveils-wireless-service-project-fi/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="engadget-fi-multiple-phone-networks">{{cite web | url=http://www.engadget.com/2015/04/22/google-project-fi/ | title=Google's Project Fi service turns multiple phone networks into one | publisher=AOL Inc. | work=Engadget | date=2015-04-04 | accessdate=2015-12-05 | author=Velazco, Chris | archive-date=2019-08-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803184031/http://www.engadget.com/2015/04/22/google-project-fi/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Google Fi的原名是Project Fi。Google于2018年11月28日将Project Fi更名为Google Fi。

== 特色 ==
服务会根据信号的强度和速度在网络之间自动切换。会自动连接到符合标准的Wi-Fi热点，并通过自动的[[虚拟专用网络|虚拟专用网络]]加密传输数据。当用户通过Wi-Fi进行通话时，网络会在覆盖不佳时无缝切换到[[蜂窩行動網路|蜂窩行動網路]]下继续通话<ref name="washingtonpost-review-remarkable-feature">{{cite web | url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-switch/wp/2015/07/08/the-most-remarkable-feature-of-googles-new-cell-service/ | title=Project Fi review: The most remarkable feature of Google’s new cell service | work=The Washington Post | date=2015-07-08 | accessdate=2015-12-05 | author=Fung, Brian | archive-date=2020-07-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711074811/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-switch/wp/2015/07/08/the-most-remarkable-feature-of-googles-new-cell-service/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="android-central-what-is-project-fi">{{cite web | url=http://www.androidcentral.com/what-project-fi-how-does-it-work-and-why-do-i-want-it | title=What is Project Fi, how does it work and why do I want it? | work=Android Central | date=2015-11-01 | accessdate=2015-12-05 | author=Martonik, Andrew | archive-date=2020-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208121825/https://www.androidcentral.com/what-project-fi-how-does-it-work-and-why-do-i-want-it | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="the-globe-and-mail-why-ditched-cellphone-carrier">{{cite web | url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/technology/tech-news/google-expanding-into-us-cellphone-plans-with-project-fi/article27443197/ | title=Why I ditched my cellphone carrier to try Google's Project Fi | publisher=The Globe and Mail Inc. | work=The Globe and Mail | date=2015-11-23 | accessdate=2015-12-05 | author=El Akkad, Omar | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108094005/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/technology/tech-news/google-expanding-into-us-cellphone-plans-with-project-fi/article27443197/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 套餐计划 ==
每月的基本资费为20美元，包括无限制的语音通话和短信，外加10美元/GB（0.01美元/MB）的数据流量，按使用量收费<ref>{{cite web | url=https://fi.google.com/about/plan/ | title=Google Fi - Plan benefits & details | publisher=Google | work=Google Fi | accessdate=2018-02-14 | archive-date=2019-09-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190910034039/https://fi.google.com/about/plan/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外Google Fi還提供無限流量套餐，每月固定费用为70美元，最多可提供22GB的高速流量数据。22GB使用完畢之后，流量速度限制为256kbps<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://support.google.com/fi/answer/6330195?hl=en|title=Use Google Fi with tablets & other compatible devices - Google Fi Help|website=support.google.com|access-date=2019-01-28|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111222656/https://support.google.com/fi/answer/6330195?hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 适用 ==
在 Project Fi 改名为 Google Fi 之前，普通的 SIM 卡仅可用于 Google 自家的 Android 设备（如 Nexus、Pixel 系列手机）以及极少数其他品牌的 Android 设备（如 Moto X 手机）上；而仅数据（Data Only）的 SIM 卡则可用于任意带蜂窝移动网络功能的设备上。

在 Project Fi 改名为 Google Fi 之后，普通的 SIM 卡已可在几乎所有品牌的手机（包括 iPhone 手机）上使用。

